      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――年始特番の二週間前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Two weeks before the New Year’s special",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_bicycle-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1439.9999857,
          "startTime": 1.4399999857
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……はぁ……ラストスパート……！\n……ふぅ、これで今日のトレーニングは終わりね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… final push…!\n…Phew. That’s the end of today’s training.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "え、{user}さん？　いつからそこに？\nすみません、集中していて気付かなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ {user}-san? Since when have you been there?\nSorry‚ I was so focused I didn’t notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "フィットネスバイク、お疲れ様\n朝から漕いでたけど、まさかずっと漕いでいたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice work on the exercise bike.\nYou’ve been pedaling since this morning… you don’t mean the whole time‚ do you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "途中で一度、休憩しました\nでも『挑戦』の本番では、休憩なんて出来ませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I did take one break along the way.\nBut during the actual “challenge‚” I won’t be able to rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5999993642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "二週間後の、新年の特番でやる『挑戦』企画か……\n瑠依は、人力飛行機で飛ぶんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The “challenge” for the New Year’s special in two weeks…\nYou’re flying a human-powered aircraft‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.7333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そうです、失敗する訳にはいきませんから\nそれに、本番では空で漕ぐんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right. I can’t afford to fail.\nAnd during the real thing‚ I’ll be pedaling in the air.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "天候や風向きだって影響するでしょうし\n練習とは、全然違うはずですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The weather and wind direction will affect it too.\nIt’ll be completely different from practice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5666660309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "だから練習では、本番の何倍も漕げるように\n鍛えておきたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I want to train until I can pedal several times more\nI will in the actual event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.2999993642,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_hungry-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5526.666666700003,
          "startTime": 62.8266660309
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "丸一日、トレーニングに専念出来るのは\n今日が最後ですし――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s the last day I can devote\nan entire day to training—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7333326976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_10_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "あ……お、お腹の音が、こんなに大きく鳴るなんて……\n……すみません、お昼ご飯、食べ忘れてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… m-my stomach is growling so loudly…\n…Sorry‚ I forgot to eat lunch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9333291371,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}